    "headline": "MAA Announces Date of Second Quarter 2026 Earnings Release, Conference Call",
    "summary": "MAA (NYSE: MAA) announced today that the Company expects to release its second quarter 2026 results on Wednesday, July 29, 2026, after market close and will hold a conference call on Thursday, July 30, 2026, at 9:00 a.m. Central Time. During the conference call, company officers will review second quarter performance and conduct a question-and-answer session.",
